high_descs: Face right, then go to the white table to your right and face the near side of the table.
Pick up the tomato from the table.
Take the tomato to the sink behind you.
Cook the tomato in the microwave above the sink.
Take the cooked tomato back to the table.
Set the tomato on the table, to the left of the pump dispenser.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooked tomato on a kitchen table.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the table with the coffee machine.
Pick up the tomato from the coffee machine.
Turn around and bring the tomato to the microwave over the sink.
Heat the tomato in the microwave.
Take the heated tomato from the microwave, turn around, bring the heated tomato to the table with the coffee machine.
Put the heated tomato on the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated tomato on the table.

high_descs: Turn right and face the white table.
Pick up the pumpkin from the table.
Turn around and go to the microwave.
Microwave the pumpkin and pick it up again.
Turn around and go back to the table.
Put the pumpkin on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked pumpkin on the table.
